data.description: Well kept 5 bd 2 bath home on almost two acres. Plenty of room inside and outside. Many mature trees with back yard fenced with a storage building and carport. Has a new roof and recently replaced air conditioner. Just freshly painted outside trim and new flooring in the master bedroom as well as freshly painted master bath. Sellers giving a $5000 flooring allowance for other flooring.
